de.tlabs.mobileCloud.benchmarkBundle2
Class pidigits

java.lang.Object
  de.tlabs.mobileCloud.benchmarkBundle2.pidigits

public class pidigits
extends java.lang.Object

Each program should use the same step-by-step spigot algorithm to calculate digits of Pi. Each program should calculate the first N digits of Pi print the digits 10-to-a-line, with the running total of digits calculated Modified for the PowerDroid framework by Andrius Aucinas

Author:
Andrius
